					</li><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><a itemprop="item" href="https://www.caricos.com/cars/"><span itemprop="name">Cars</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="2" />
							</li><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><a itemprop="item" href="https://www.caricos.com/cars/volvo.html"><span itemprop="name">Volvo</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="3" />
							</li><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><h1 itemprop="name">Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY</h1><meta itemprop="position" content="4" />
							</li></ol><div id="bgimg"><img src="https://images.caricos.com/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/1920x1080/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge_1_1920x1080.jpg" alt="2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge" ></div></div><section class="narrow"><article><div id="article-body"  itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article"><div id="article-info"><time itemprop="datePublished">Published: Oct 16, 2019</time><time itemprop="dateModified">Modified: Oct 16, 2019</time><div>By: <span itemprop="author">Caricos Editors</span></div><input type="hidden" itemprop="publisher" value="Caricos.com"><input type="hidden" itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" value="https://www.caricos.com/cars/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/"></div><div itemprop="articleBody"><h2 itemprop="headline">An Electrifying Step Forward: The 2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge</h2>
<p>In a world where the question is not if, but when you will switch to an electric vehicle, Volvo takes a leap into the future with the introduction of its first-ever fully electric car - the 2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge. This new addition to Volvo's fleet represents more than just a car; it is a clear declaration of the company's commitment to electrification and a critical step in its new Recharge line concept.</p>
<h3>Building on Success</h3>
<p>The XC40 Recharge isn't a departure from Volvo's successful model, but an extension. It's based on the widely acclaimed and best-selling XC40 small SUV, retaining its winning formula while incorporating a fresh, electric twist. Notably, the XC40 Recharge is the first Volvo to be equipped with an infotainment system powered by Google’s Android operating system, marking another first for the car manufacturer.</p>
<img itemprop="image" style="width:100%" alt="Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY |  P8 AWD (Color:Glacier Silver) | Front Three-Quarter" src="https://images.caricos.com/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/2560x1440/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge_3_2560x1440.jpg"><h3>The Path to Electrification</h3>
<p>Volvo has been vocal about its electric future. The introduction of the XC40 Recharge is not a solitary initiative, but the beginning of a new era of fully electric Volvos. Over the next five years, Volvo plans to roll out a new electric car annually, aiming to make all-electric cars account for half of its global sales by 2025, with the remainder being hybrids.</p>
<h3>Recharge: A New Approach to Electric Mobility</h3>
<p>Recharge will become the overarching brand for all Volvo's electric and plug-in hybrid vehicles. Beginning from 2020, potential customers visiting the Volvo Cars website will have to decide whether they want a Volvo Recharge model or not, signifying a clear shift towards promoting electric mobility. The company even plans to incentivize customers with an offer of free electricity for a year for every Recharge plug-in hybrid model purchased.</p>
<h3>Performance Meets Sustainability</h3>
<p>Driving the XC40 Recharge doesn't mean compromising on performance. The vehicle offers a state-of-the-art, all-wheel-drive powertrain that produces 408 horsepower and boasts a range of over 400 km (WLTP) on a single charge. The battery's fast-charge system allows for 80% capacity in approximately 40 minutes. The XC40 Recharge represents a satisfying blend of Volvo's safety, comfort, and performance, now combined with advanced electric capabilities.</p>
<img itemprop="image" style="width:100%" alt="Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY |  P8 AWD (Color:Glacier Silver) | Rear Three-Quarter" src="https://images.caricos.com/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/2560x1440/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge_20_2560x1440.jpg"><h3>Expanding the Recharge Family</h3>
<p>Each model in Volvo's line-up now includes a Recharge option, with Volvo being the only manufacturer to provide a plug-in variant for each model. The XC40 Recharge is not a standalone effort, but the beginning of an extensive family of electric and hybrid vehicles. Volvo's ambitious roadmap is a tangible testament to its commitment to the Paris climate agreement and a climate-neutral future.</p>
<h3>Final Thoughts</h3>
<p>The 2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge is a vehicle that speaks volumes about the company's electric ambitions. It is a potent blend of the conventional qualities Volvo has always been known for - safety, style, and innovation, now powered by cutting-edge electric technology. While it may just be one model, the XC40 Recharge symbolizes Volvo's electrifying future, and if this is any indication of what's to come, the future looks very promising indeed.</p>
<h6>-Ed</h6><p class="in-article-collage"><img itemprop="image" src="https://img3.caricos.com/collage/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge_0.jpg" alt="2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge"><span>2020 Volvo XC40 Recharge</span></p></div></div><div id="navmj"><div id="navpgmj"><div style="margin: 0 0 0 auto;"><a href="https://www.caricos.com/cars/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/#1" id="pgnprev" class="prevnext prev off" title="Previous Page"><span></span></a></div><select id="page-select" label=""><label for="page-select" style="display:none;">Select a Page</label><option value="1">Page 1 / 4</option><option value="2">Page 2 / 4</option><option value="3">Page 3 / 4</option><option value="4">Page 4 / 4</option></select><div style="margin: 0 auto 0 0;"><a href="https://www.caricos.com/cars/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/#2" id="pgnnext" class="prevnext next pna" title="Next Page"><span></span></a></div></div><div id="modelimgnavmj" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageGallery"><div id="galmj" style="width: 400%; left: 0%;"><div class="galpage" id="galpage1" style="width:25%"><div class="modelimgviewmj" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><a itemprop="contentUrl" class="modelimgviewimg" href="https://images.caricos.com/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/2560x1440/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge_1_2560x1440.jpg" style="font-size:0.7rem;"><span itemprop="caption">Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY |  P8 AWD (Color:Glacier Silver) | Front Three-Quarter</span></a><a class="modelimgviewimg" title="Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY |  P8 AWD (Color:Glacier Silver) | Front Three-Quarter" href="https://www.caricos.com/cars/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/1.html"><img class="galprev" alt="Volvo XC40 Recharge | 2020MY |  P8 AWD (Color:Glacier Silver) | Front Three-Quarter" data-src="https://images.caricos.com/v/volvo/2020_volvo_xc40_recharge/images/gallery_1.jpg?1571252606"></a></div><div class="modelimgviewmj" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/